tyle="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px;"><br></div></div><div style="box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(114, 114, 114); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><div style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px;"><div data-elementor-type="wp-post" data-elementor-id="4823" data-elementor-settings="[]" style="box-sizing: inherit; hyphens: manual;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-id="3a4a538" data-element_type="section" style="box-sizing: border-box; display: block; position: relative;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; position: relative; max-width: 100%;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 1160px; display: flex;"><div data-id="b12e115" data-element_type="column" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; min-height: 1px; display: flex; width: 1160px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 1160px; position: relative; display: flex; padding: 0px 10px 10px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; width: 1140px; flex-wrap: wrap; align-content: flex-start; display: flex;"><div data-id="7c752be" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; width: 1140px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: background 0.3s ease 0s, border 0.3s ease 0s, border-radius 0.3s ease 0s, box-shadow 0.3s ease 0s, -webkit-border-radius 0.3s ease 0s, -webkit-box-shadow 0.3s ease 0s;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box;"><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">PMTI ekspertlari o&lsquo;zbekistonlik mehnat muhojirlari uchun yangi yo&lsquo;nalishlarni baholadi.</em></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">2021 yil</strong> yakunlariga ko&lsquo;ra O&lsquo;zbekistonga o&lsquo;tkazilgan pul mablag&lsquo;lari hajmi&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">8,1 milliard AQSH dollari</strong>ni tashkil qilgan. Buning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">70 foizi yoki 5,6 milliard dollari</strong> Rossiya Federatsiyasidan o&lsquo;tkazilgan. O&lsquo;sha yili Rossiyadagi o&lsquo;zbekistonlik mehnat muhojirlari soni (Bandlik va mehnat munosabatlari vazirligi ma&rsquo;lumotlariga ko&lsquo;ra)&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">1 036 305 kishi</strong>ni tashkil qilgan.&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">2021 yilda</strong> har bir mehnat muhojirining oylik o&lsquo;tkazmasi&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">453 AQSH dollari</strong>ni tashkil qilgan.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Emigratsion tuzoq mamlakatning iqtisodiy barqarorligi ko&lsquo;p jihatdan muhojirlar o&lsquo;tkazadigan pul mablag&lsquo;i, binobarin o&lsquo;sha mamlakatning migratsion siyosatiga bog&lsquo;liq bo&lsquo;lgan bir vaziyatni tavsiflaydi. Muhojirlarni uyga qaytishga majbur qiluvchi har qanday iqtisodiy bo&lsquo;hron mamlakatdagi ishsizlar sonini keskin oshiradi va pul mablag&lsquo;larining kelmay qolishi kambag&lsquo;allikni yanada kuchaytiradi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">PMTI ekspertlari muhojirlar oqimiga ta&rsquo;sir qiluvchi tashqi omillarni inobatga olgan holda tashqi mehnat muhojirligi imkoniyatlarini baholash bo&lsquo;yicha tahlil o&lsquo;tkazdi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Tahlil natijasida quyidagi asosiy xulosalar chiqarildi:</strong></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">-&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">ingliz tilini bilish, diplomatik vakolatxonaning mavjudligi, aviachiptalar narxi, shuningdek, borayotgan mamlakatda YAIMning aholi jon boshiga ulushi</strong> mehnat muhojirligi uchun muhim omillar ekanligi ma&rsquo;lum bo&lsquo;ldi;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">- donor mamlakatda diplomatik vakolatxonaning mavjudligi mehnat muhojirlarining ketishini 16 foizga oshiradi;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">- donor mamlakatlardagi ingliz tilini bilish talabi O&lsquo;zbekistondan ketayotgan mehnat muhojirlari oqimini 55 foizga kamaytiradi;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">- imkoniyat 8 foizdan 80 foizgacha bo&lsquo;lgan&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Polsha, Bolgariya, Litva, Chexiya, Fransiya, Germaniya va Buyuk Britaniya</strong> kabi mamlakatlar o&lsquo;zbekistonlik mehnat muhojirlari uchun eng maqbul yo&lsquo;nalishlar bo&lsquo;lishi mumkin;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">-&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Singapur, Saudiya Arabistoni va Yaponiya</strong> kabi mamlakatlar 4 foizdan 49 foizgacha imkoniyatga ega.&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Ozarbayjon va Belarus</strong> Respublikasi MDH mamlakatlari orasida eng katta imkoniyatga ega ekanligi ma&rsquo;lum bo&lsquo;ldi.</h3><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(114, 114, 114);"><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" height="904" src="https://imrs.uz/public/ckfinder/userfiles/files/uzb(2).jpg" width="1280" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: none; height: auto; max-width: 100%; border-radius: 0px; box-shadow: none;" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Ko&lsquo;p jihatdan Rossiyadagi mehnat muhojirlari o&lsquo;tkazadigan pul mablag&lsquo;lariga bog&lsquo;lanib qolish nafaqat mehnat bozori, balki butun respublikadagi vaziyatni yanada chuqurlashtiradi. Shu sabablar tufayli ayni chog&lsquo;da&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">ishchi kuchini eksport qilish</strong> uchun yangi imkoniyatlarni ko&lsquo;rib chiqish zarur. Shuni qayd etish joizki, O&lsquo;zbekistondan asosan malaka darajasi yuqori bo&lsquo;lmagan, o&lsquo;rta-maxsus ta&rsquo;limga ega ishchilar ketmoqda. Ular asosan qishloq xo&lsquo;jaligi, qurilish va qisman xizmat ko&lsquo;rsatish (sotuvchilar, bemorga qarovchilar, farroshlar va boshqalar) sohalarida mehnat qilmoqda. Bugungi kunda O&lsquo;zbekiston dunyodagi 27 ta mamlakat<a href="https://imrs.uz/publications/articles-and-abstracts/migration1#_ftn1" name="_ftnref1" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; box-shadow: none;">[1]</a> bilan mehnat bitimlariga ega. Shunga qaramay, Rossiya, Qozog&lsquo;iston va Turkiya o&lsquo;zbekistonlik mehnat muhojirlari yo&lsquo;l olayotgan asosiy mamlakatlar bo&lsquo;lib qolmoqda. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">PMTI ekspertlari tashqi mehnat muhojirligi imkoniyatlaridan foydalanishni baholash uchun xalqaro miqyosda ishchi kuchining ketishi (dunyodagi 40 ta mamlakat bo&lsquo;yicha 2017-2019 yillarga oid ma&rsquo;lumotlar) gravitatsion model qo&lsquo;llanildi. Bunda mehnat bitimlari, diplomatik vakolatxonalarning borligi, inflyatsiya, ishsizlik darajasi, o&lsquo;rtacha oylik maosh, aviachiptalar narxi, savdo sherikchiligi, vizalarning mavjudligi, Toshkent va boshqa davlatlarning poytaxtlari orasidagi masofa, inson salohiyatini &nbsp;rivojlantirish indeksi, ingliz tilini bilish indeksi, umumiy din kabi ko&lsquo;rsatkichlardan ham foydalanildi.</h3><table align="left" cellspacing="0" style="box-sizing: border-box; border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; width: 623px;"><tbody style="box-sizing: border-box;"><tr style="box-sizing: border-box;"><td style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black; background-color: rgb(251, 228, 213); height: 187px; vertical-align: top; width: 623px;"><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Qo&lsquo;shimcha: Gravitatsion model</strong> (lot.<em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">gravitas</em> &mdash; &nbsp;og&lsquo;irlik, kuch, harakat) &mdash; makondagi ob&rsquo;ektlar (shaharlar, hududlar, mamlakatlar) ijtimoiy-iqtisodiy munosabatlarni tavsiflaydi. Huddi shu modelning turli xil ko&lsquo;rinishlari urbanizatsiya jarayoni, sanoat korxonalarini joylashtirish, eksport va import o&lsquo;rtasidagi o&lsquo;zaro aloqa, aholi ko&lsquo;chishini tadqiq qilishda foydalaniladi.&nbsp;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Model tenglamalari quyidagicha:</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">KETISH</em><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">ij</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">=</em></strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">&beta;</em></strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">1</em></strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">+</em></strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">&beta;</em></strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">2</em></strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">ln</em></strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">GDP</em></strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">+</em></strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">&beta;</em></strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">3</em></strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">lnticket+</em></strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">&beta;</em></strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">4</em></strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">DIP</em></strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">+&nbsp;</em></strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">&beta;</em></strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">5</em></strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">Eng</em></strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">.</em></strong></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">Ketish&nbsp;</em></strong>&ndash; &nbsp;mehnat muhojirlarining 2017-2019 yillar oralig&lsquo;ida j mamlakatdan i mamlakatga ketishi;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">lnGDP&nbsp;</em></strong>&ndash; &nbsp;YAIMning aholi jon boshiga ulushi;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">Lnticket&nbsp;</em></strong>&ndash; &nbsp;aviachiptalar narxi;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Soxta o&lsquo;zgaruvchan&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">DIP</em></strong>&ndash; diplomatik vakolatxonalarning mavjudligi;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">Eng&nbsp;</em></strong>&ndash; &nbsp; donor mamlakatlarda ingliz tilining mavjudligi.</h3></td></tr></tbody></table><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Hisob-kitoblarga ko&lsquo;ra, donor mamlakatlarda YAIMning aholi jon boshiga nisbatan 1 foiz o&lsquo;sishi O&lsquo;zbekistondan mehnat muhojirlarining ketishini&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">0,7 foiz&nbsp;</strong>oshiradi. Aviachiptalar narxining 1 foizga oshishi, mehnat migratsiyasini&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">1,35 foizga&nbsp;</strong>pasaytiradi. Donor mamlakatlarda diplomatik vakolatxonalarning borligi mehnat muhojirlarining ketishini&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">16 foizga</strong> oshiradi. Donor mamlakatlardagi ingliz tilini bilish talabi O&lsquo;zbekistondan mehnat muhojirlarining ketishini&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">55 foizga</strong> kamaytiradi.&nbsp;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Mehnat muhojirlarining ketish modeli asosida bundan keyin xalqaro mehnat migratsiyasini rivojlantirishning ancha&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">istiqbolli bo&lsquo;lgan bozorlari</strong> aniqlandi. Demak, gravitatsiya modeli bo&lsquo;yicha bu imkoniyat Buyuk Britaniya va Yevropa Ittifoqining an&rsquo;anaviy asosiy donor mamlakatlarida qo&lsquo;shimcha&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">8 foizdan 80 foizgacha</strong> deb baholanmoqda.&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Polsha, Bolgariya, Litva, Chexiya, Fransiya, Germaniya va Buyuk Britaniya</strong> kabi mamlakatlar mehnat migratsiyasini rivojlantirishning eng maqbul yo&lsquo;nalishlaridir.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Singapur, Saudiya Arabistoni va Yaponiya</strong> kabi mamlaktalar<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;4 foizdan 49 foizgacha</strong> imkoniyatga ega.&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Ozarbayjon va Belarus Respublikasi</strong> MDH mamlakatlari orasida eng katta imkoniyatga ega ekanligi ma&rsquo;lum bo&lsquo;ldi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">PMTI ekspertlari</strong> amalga oshirilgan hisob-kitoblar nnatijasida&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">chora-tadbirlar va mexanizmlar</strong>ni tatbiq etish bo&lsquo;yicha shunday takliflarni ishlab chiqdi:</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">1. Xorijiy mamlakatlar bilan diplomatik, xususan ishchi kuchini eksport qilish sohasidagi kelishuvlarni kengaytirish, mehnat shartnomalarini tuzish va mehnat qilayotgan muhojirlarning huquqlarini himoya qilish.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">2. Maktabdan boshlab xorijiy tillarni, ayniqsa ingliz tilini o&lsquo;rgatishni sifat jihatidan yaxshilash. Mehnat muhojirligiga jo&lsquo;nash istagida bo&lsquo;lgan ko&lsquo;psonli fuqarolarni ingliz tili kurslari bilan qamrab olish, mahallalarda ingliz tilini o&lsquo;rgatish bo&lsquo;yicha bepul kurslarni tashkil etish.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">3. Aviachiptalarni xarid qilishda Bandlikka ko&lsquo;maklashish jamg&lsquo;armasi yordamida chipta bahosining 50 foizini to&lsquo;lash yo&lsquo;li orqali mehnat muhojirlariga imtiyozlarni taqdim etish.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">4. Bandlik va mehnat munosabatlari vazirligi mehnat muhojirlarini jo&lsquo;natish uchun muhim, deb hisoblangan mamlakatlarning mehnat bozorini muntazam ravishda chuqur tahlil qilib borishi zarur.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">5. O&lsquo;zbekistondan chiqib ketayotgan mehnat muhojirlari haqidagi rasmiy hisobotni takomillashtirish zarur (chunki alohida vazirliklarning raqamlarida tafovut mavjud).</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">6. Yevropa Ittifoqi mamlakatlariga ishga jo&lsquo;natuvchi xususiy bandlik agentliklari uchun litsenziya olishni soddalashtirish.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Muhabbat Ahmedova<br style="box-sizing: border-box;">PMTI guruh rahbari</strong></h3><hr style="box-sizing: border-box; height: 1px; background-color: transparent; border: 0px; margin: 0px;"><h5 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><a href="https://imrs.uz/publications/articles-and-abstracts/migration1#_ftnref1" name="_ftn1" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; box-shadow: none;">[1]</a>Rossiya, Qozog&lsquo;iston, Belarus Respublikasi, BAA, Turkiya, Tojikiston, Bolgariya, Chexiya Respublikasi, Latviya, Polsha, Quvayt, Germaniya, Shveysariya, Gollandiya, Isroil, Yaponiya, Slovakiya, Saudiya Arabistoni, Litva, Baxrayn, Ukraina, Malayziya, Qirg&lsquo;iziston, Ozarbayjon, Xorvatiya, Finlyandiya, O&lsquo;mon</h5></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section></div></div></div><div style="box-sizing: inherit;">&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: inherit;"><i class="bi bi-eye"></i> 3855</span></div></div></div></header></header><div style="box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(114, 114, 114); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><br></div>
